Members Exchange (MEMX) is searching for a Data Scientist to become part of an innovative team that analyses exchange and industry data and presents information in a meaningful way to a variety of audiences. This role will collaborate with many departments across MEMX including Development, Member Experience, Finance, and Strategy. This is a great opportunity for the successful candidate to become a part of a growing function and help develop tools that will meet the needs of our members and differentiate MEMX in the industry. The ideal candidate will have a passion for data exploration and analysis.

Responsibilities
Research and analyze large data sets using a variety of techniques;
Document approach and technique;
Creation and maintenance of a report library for internal and external consumption;
Present results using modern APIs and data visualiztion technologies.
Requirements
Degree in Data Science or related discipline preferred (Computer Science, Engineering, Mathematics or Statistics);
3+ years of experience in similar roles;
Knowledge of US Equities market structure and industry data models;
Experienced in analysis of large time series data sets;
Versed in mathematical modeling and statistics;
Programming skills: practiced in the use of languages such as Python, Java, R, C++.
Use of modern cloud data storage, access, and visualization methods;
Good communication and data presentation skills;
Excellent pattern recognition and predictive modeling skills;
Ability to work effectively in a very high paced, start-up environment;
Excellent written and verbal communication skills;
Should be able to work both individually and collaboratively in teams.
Benefits
At MEMX you will have the ability to work with a talented team of professionals who bring diversity of thought and background. You will have the opportunity to shape the future of our company and the impact MEMX will have on our clients and the broader markets. We offer competitive employee benefits and perks and will continue to make this a priority to attract the best.

